  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_4' aria-label=\" All India Judges Association and Others versus Union of India and Others pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('4','2025','2025_5_1070_1115','2025INSC735'); ><font size='4'> <strong>ALL INDIA JUDGES ASSOCIATION AND OTHERS<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>UNION OF INDIA AND OTHERS </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 5 S.C.R. 1070</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 735</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010005812025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : BHUSHAN RAMKRISHNA GAVAI<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, AUGUSTINE GEORGE MASIH, K. VINOD CHANDRAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Matter pertains to restoration of 10% quota reserved for Limited Departmental Competitive Examination-LDCE Judicial Service-cadre of District Judge, to 25%; reduction of the minimum qualifying experience for appearing in LDCE, and if so, by how many years; percentage of reservation of quota for meritorious candidate from the Civil Judge (Junior Division) to Civil Judge (Senior Division); the minimum<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 20-05-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> WRIT PETITION (CIVIL) No. 1022/1989</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Directions issued</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 3 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('4','2025','2025_5_1070_1115','2025INSC735','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick